OL,5, High-profile presenters should be      
OL,6, allowed to express views on issues and 
OL,7, policies but stop short of political   
OL,8, campaigning, a new BBC report says.    
OL,10,FNew rules have been published for BBC  
OL,11,Fflagship presenters following a row    
OL,12,Fover Gary Lineker's social media posts.
OL,14,FIt comes after a review into BBC social
OL,15,Fmedia guidelines was published by      
OL,16,Fformer ITN boss John Hardie.           
OL,18,FLineker responded on X, formerly       
OL,19,FTwitter, by saying the new rules were  
OL,20,F"all very sensible".                   
